  "id": "rizette",
  "name": "Rizette",
  "title": "The Cerulean Crestbearer",
  "description": "\"Riz? Are you sure you're okay?\"\n\n\"What do you mean?\"\n\n\"With this Cerulean Crest thing... Everything happened so suddenly. How do you feel about all of it?\"\n\n\"Theo... You're sweet. But I'm okay, really. I wanted the power to fight, and now I have it. And besides...\"\n\n\"Besides?\"\n\n\"Now Finn doesn't have to bear everything alone. He put his life on the line to help us when he didn't even know us, and he ended up with the responsibility of the Crimson Crest. If there's something I can do to lessen his burden, I'll do it.\"\n\n\"Riz...\"\n\n",
